    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "You can't change the configuration once it's started. But that can be fixed (everything can be fixed).\n\nEven if we consider it's possible with events and change of configuration, it is a lot of code (with respect to the declarative aspect of the rest of the API) that the user has to create to get the proper behavior. We would need a good recipe book.\n",
