    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "> I would go for this for now then.\n\nYes for the sort by price it makes sense.\n\nBut here is another use case: I would love to use such widget to create a dropdown-menu filter:\n\nSort by:\n\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td>...</td>\n<td>v</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\nBy relevance<br />\nOnly popular<br />\nOnly whatever\n</tr>\n</table>\n\nThe \"Only popular\" would target the same index than \"Default\", but add a numeric filter `popularity>1000`. I already implemented such thing. It can be another widget however.\n",
