    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "We could have a menu that is a partial state object setter. For example \n\n``` js\nvar myConfigSetterMenu = configSetterMenu({\n  config: {\n    'By relevance': {index: 'index1'},\n    'Only popular': {index: 'index2', numericFilters:{attr1:{'>': [1000]}}}\n  }\n});\n```\n\nSomething like that maybe?\n",
