    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Can also be something like that (we still need to think about how to \"revert\"):\n\n```\nsearch.addWidget(\n  instantsearch.widgets.filteringMenu({\n    container: '#filtering-selector',\n    filters: [\n      { label: 'By relevance' },\n      {\n        label: 'Only popular',\n        configure: function(helper) {\n            helper.addNumericRefinement(\"popularity\", \">\", 1000);\n        }\n      },\n    ],\n    cssClass: 'form-control'\n  })\n);\n```\n",
